.modal-header
  button(type="button", class="close", data-dismiss="modal", aria-hidden="true") &times;
  h4(class="modal-title") Bookmarklets
.modal-body.modal-bookmarklet-content
  p
    b Bookmarklets are useful to quickly save the current tab to Browserpipe.
  p Installing our bookmarklets is very easy, just select which one you want and drag and drop the orange dashed box to the bookmarks toolbar of your browser. To use it, click the generated link in the bookmarks toolbar. You can install all of them if you want.
  .bookmarklet
    a.bookmarklet-link(href='javascript:<%= archiveCode %>') ✚ Archive Browserpipe
    it allows to select the folder to archive the tab
  .bookmarklet
    a.bookmarklet-link(href='javascript:<%= laterCode %>') ✚ Later Browserpipe
    it saves the the tab for later in Browserpipe
  .bookmarklet
    a.bookmarklet-link(href='javascript:<%= openCode %>') ✚ Open Browserpipe
    it saves and open the tab in Browserpipe
.modal-footer
  button(type="button", class="orange-btn", data-dismiss="modal") Close
